snippet: AC Milan played down problems with their flight as they finally left for Qatar on Wednesday, nearly one day behind schedule, to face Juventus in Friday's Italian Supercup match....
lead_paragraph: AC Milan played down problems with their flight as they finally left for Qatar on Wednesday, nearly one day behind schedule, to face Juventus in Friday's Italian Supercup match.

headline.main: Milan Play Down Travel Problems Ahead of Delayed Flight to Qatar
